These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
Movie-Genre: documentary, comedy, mystery, satire
Music-Genre: hip-hop, reggae, house, jazz
1. Music-Genre:reggae is on the left of Music-Genre:hip-hop##1
2. Movie-Genre:documentary == Music-Genre:jazz##1
3. Music-Genre:house is on the right of Music-Genre:hip-hop##1
4. Movie-Genre:comedy is on the left of Music-Genre:jazz##1
5. Movie-Genre:satire is on the left of Music-Genre:hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre          | satire | mystery | comedy | documentary   |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | hip-hop     | house   | jazz |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
Color: light-blue, fuchsia, white, lavender
House: victorian, colonial, modern, craftsman
1. Color:lavender == House:colonial##1
2. Color:light-blue is on the far right##1
3. Color:fuchsia is on the right of Color:lavender##1
4. Color:lavender is on the right of House:modern##1
5. House:colonial is on the left of House:victorian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | white | lavender | fuchsia | light-blue    |
| House   | modern    | colonial      | victorian | craftsman |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
Flower: orchid, iris, zinnia, balloon-flower
Beverage: tea, fanta, almond-milk, 7up
1. Beverage:almond-milk is on the left of Beverage:7up##1
2. Flower:orchid == Beverage:tea##1
3. Beverage:fanta is on the far right##1
4. Beverage:7up is on the right of Flower:balloon-flower##1
5. Flower:zinnia is on the left of Beverage:fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Flower         | orchid | balloon-flower | zinnia   | iris |
| Beverage   | tea   | almond-milk | 7up | fanta         |

