2. Movie-Genre:spy is on the right of Movie-Genre:adventure##1
3. City:nizza is on the right of City:rome##1
4. City:san-francisco is on the far left##1
5. City:venice == Movie-Genre:adventure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| City      | san-francisco | venice  | rome | nizza |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | adventure | spy           | musical   |

