.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
Color: blue, light-blue, white, blood-red
Movie-Genre: action, romance, martial-arts, scientific
1. Movie-Genre:action is on the left of Color:light-blue##1
2. Movie-Genre:romance is on the left of Color:blood-red##1
3. Color:blue is on the left of Color:white##1
4. Color:blood-red == Movie-Genre:scientific##1
5. Movie-Genre:action is on the left of Color:light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Color   | blue | white | light-blue | blood-red   |
| Movie-Genre     | martial-arts  | action    | romance       | scientific |

 